Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐江 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 快要崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐江姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想相信大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋葉星的人們一直以來都支持著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 受到他們溫暖的聲援和笑容的鼓勵 我們才能走到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使被他們討厭 我還是想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信那天所獲贈的善意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 對這樣一無是處的我也肯說喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是超級大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不信的話 會遭報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該說你積極 還是消極呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜禮貌正確地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓大家面帶微笑 變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 小楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家面帶微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個大家 也包括我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 現在也許是敵人的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也許不能溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 總有一天說不定能相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾回去 滾回去 滾回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara的光芒這麼耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使被怨恨 被攻擊 你也義無反顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得如此堅強了啊 凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊醬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又見面了 優子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是被先聖老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是通過Kirara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由雙晶素召集的生命體的集體無意識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召喚到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集體無意識…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果演藝在宇宙中消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:04:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們的內心將會完全失去光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 與雙晶素共鳴的集體無意識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不被DES魔掌所波及的時間夾縫中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將Center Nova們召集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 我們在這裡歌唱著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了人的無意識深處不被深深的絕望吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持續點亮希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當這光芒消失的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們的內心就會被黑暗吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 優子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於你們在現實世界中保護了演藝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許能夠迴避那樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的 就憑我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得到的 優子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就永遠也不能再在啊醬身邊唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想超越啊醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成為比啊醬更閃耀的Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 其實只是想在憧憬的前田敦子身邊唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前田敦子的話就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別被騙了 她們可是背叛我們的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對 別扯淡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾出秋葉星！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於我們從秋葉星的暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招從而致大家的誤解 我們表示萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼下去有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們回到故鄉一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}滾回去 滾回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是沒法溝通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想傳達歌聲 傳達愛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭我們也沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使討厭我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也請別討厭歌聲和演藝！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛那瞬間凪沙變成啊醬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直是那麼地嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從她們身上獲得了許多的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從古至今 代表著每一個時代的藝人們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AKB0048
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決不能就此在我們這一代斷送
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高燒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 難道是襲名發熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是凪沙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特設演唱會舞臺的防衛線被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是凪沙的身體頂得住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 友歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我就想在這裡歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才算是我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 凪沙 一起來鼓起陣風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我的資料庫中把拍攝的景象投影到會場中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子 門的另一面是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經消失的Center Nova會照亮心中的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以由我們照亮現在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13代啊醬是如此跟我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊醬說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋葉星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們喜歡秋葉星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被埋怨 就算被憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
